textBeforeTable: Finn Pendant features an Opal diffuser with a Dark Smoke, Bronze, or Black finish. Available in three adjustable lengths. One 100 watt, 120 volt A19 type Medium base incandescent bulb is required, but not included. UL listed. 18.2 inch width x 14.4 inch height. Short Length: overall length adjustable from 21.8 - 27.6 inches. Standard Length: overall length adjustable from 27.3 - 38.2 inches. Long Length: overall length adjustable from 37.6 - 59.4 inches.
